We keep contribution pathways clear and inclusive. Whether you write code, improve docs, shape the roadmap, or validate operations patterns, you help Sonicverse stay transparent and useful.

{% checklist title="Contribution lanes" eyebrow="Ways to help" %}

- **Core products**: Streaming, workflow, and observability platform layers
- **Ecosystem**: Integrations, plugins, starter templates, and deployment patterns
- **Documentation**: Tutorials, migration guides, and architecture explainers
- **Community**: Translation, moderation, support, and roadmap feedback

{% /checklist %}
